00:35:31.575 --> 00:35:32.575
Okay?

00:35:39.845 --> 00:35:40.885
That's when I knew.

00:35:42.855 --> 00:35:44.415
That my Min Ho was dead.

00:35:46.985 --> 00:35:48.085
Those jerks...

00:35:50.395 --> 00:35:53.195
had killed my son.

00:36:01.865 --> 00:36:02.935
Dong Su.

