Go Eun, when you have a chance, can you look into...

00:49:38.485 --> 00:49:40.025
where Im Dong Hyeon's money is coming from?

00:49:40.585 --> 00:49:43.355
I don't really have time. But I'll see what I can do.

00:49:43.425 --> 00:49:45.325
(Fitness in All in Gym)

00:49:45.995 --> 00:49:46.995
Eun Seo.

00:49:47.365 --> 00:49:48.565
You're here, Mr. Im?

00:49:48.895 --> 00:49:49.965
Any cash come in?

00:49:50.195 --> 00:49:53.235
Yes, today was sign-ups for the new K-pop dance class.

00:49:56.205 --> 00:49:59.175
Looks like a good turnout. You have all the cash ready, right?

00:49:59.505 --> 00:50:00.805
Yes, I've got it all right here.

00:50:01.805 --> 00:50:02.905
Heading out again?

00:50:04.015 --> 00:50:05.914
Yes. If anyone asks, tell them I'm at a funeral.

00:50:05.915 --> 00:50:07.015
See you later.

00:50:07.545 --> 00:50:10.055
Mr. Im!

00:50:11.085 --> 00:50:12.485
Unbelievable.

00:50:12.815 --> 00:50:16.455
So much here needs to be fixed, but he grabs the cash and leaves.

00:50:16.525 --> 00:50:19.255
Driver Kim Do Gi, you have a fare waiting outside.

00:50:19.325 --> 00:50:22.095
(Fitness in All in Gym)

00:50:24.035 --> 00:50:25.495
There's no door handle?

00:50:26.705 --> 00:50:27.805
What?

00:50:29.605 --> 00:50:30.935
(Deluxe Taxi)

00:50:32.305 --> 00:50:34.405
Driver! Let's go, step on it.

00:50:36.105 --> 00:50:37.875
Yes, I'm on my way back now.

00:50:38.345 --> 00:50:40.085
Don't touch my stuff. Just leave it.

00:50:40.185 --> 00:50:42.645
And tell the other guys I'll be there in a minute.

00:50:42.885 --> 00:50:43.885
Got it?

00:50:44.915 --> 00:50:46.255
Darn it, this is so frustrating.

